description:
The Hungarian Nightmare is back and she wants to be the
ultimate surrender champion. She is not happy with
just winning - she is only happy if her opponent is
totally defeated, made to submit, and gets finger
fucked during the match. If you lose to her, you know
you're getting fucked brutally in Rd4.
The Gymnast is tall, muscular, and ripped. With six
pack abs and legs of steel, she enjoys getting weaker
opponents to submit to her crushing leg
scissors. Her legs scissors have gotten her 13
submissions this season. She is strong and powerful;
however, the nightmare has her spooked and unsure of
herself.
The winner of this match will go on to wrestle Live on
Aug 21 in the Summer Vengeance Quarter finals.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE
